{"type": "article", "id": 32974, "title": "装个柜子而已，你可别密恐啊｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-07T23:02:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33182, "name": "紙可拍"}, {"id": 33183, "name": "原質東隅"}, {"id": 33629, "name": "Sabrina Fossi Design"}, {"id": 33630, "name": "Vibia"}, {"id": 33631, "name": "Arik Levy"}, {"id": 33632, "name": "Shigeki Yamamoto"}, {"id": 33633, "name": "Herr Bürli"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161007225036Nrp5b37OU1ncaV4Q.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>North by Arik Levy</h3><p>以色列裔法国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.ariklevy.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Arik Levy</a> 最近为巴塞罗那灯具公司 <a href=\"http://www.vibia.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vibia</a> 设计了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.vibia.com/en/lamparas-north/\" rel=\"nofollow\">North</a> 的灯具，形似斗笠的灯罩通过细线与修长的支架相连，营造出相当独特的照明效果。Levy 为 North 设计了多种支撑结构，使灯具能够根据需要在落地灯、壁灯和吊灯间转换，或者是提供局部的照明效果。这种灵活性使灯具既能胜任私人住宅，也能应用在公共空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220111MHKs0tXULq25bVP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770171\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220111Jts8573lR12VDeSX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220112MOhJdBbjq947gLFi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220112bzlcZeCg2M6uhGaS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.832518\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610072201110d9yNKqjkvLowZPX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.842298\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610072201121qDLTbs3Z5yu9F2Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985330\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Play Sideboard by Shigeki Yamamoto</h3><p>和其他围绕着木材开展创作的设计师不同，日裔德国设计师 <a href=\"http://shigekiyamamoto.com/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shigeki Yamamoto</a> 抱着为日常生活带来趣味的 high humor design 设计理念，打造了一系列极具创意的作品。他的最新作品是这件名为 Play Sideboard 的柜子，用户需要将各种覆有玻璃油的橡木块零件拼接起来。Yamamoto 希望通过这种特殊的 DIY 体验让人们回忆起儿时玩过的积木，重新发现自己的创造力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220141BSpOD5vsf8WlbRYx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220141zYf1bHcLFJhTQjpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220141GmLdDrh2RoMeNgJn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220141tFQXDBWcjZHNnKwz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220141IBgeCbAr8dQMZxqf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Energy Pet by Suki Lee</h3><p>如果你喜欢动物造型的移动电源，由深圳设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/sukiflam\" rel=\"nofollow\">Suki Lee</a> 带来的这款 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42789745/Energy-Pet\" rel=\"nofollow\">Energy Pet</a> 移动电源概念设计或许会让你眼前一亮。它包含了小熊、小狗和小象三种动物造型，眼睛则特意设计成了两道闪电。为了支撑智能设备，它们的身体被“拉长”了，小短腿的底部附有吸盘，头部也能根据需要进行转动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220224XrKvnke0ayVjGZhO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220224XI9SZlJVaLRmNTdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220224wy3EQ8F4fCOYBvXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220225yWuaeSbxo6h9BPF3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220225ClKeShEduDmLVIrw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>CROZ by Paper Shoot &amp; Hylé design</h3><p>还记得我们之前介绍的透明数码相机 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32651.html\">CROZ</a> 吗？在众筹失败之后，<a href=\"http://www.papershoot.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">紙可拍</a>与<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hyledesignmacau/\" rel=\"nofollow\">原質東隅</a>又上线了木制版的 CROZ，截至目前已经成功筹到了目标资金。透明的外壳被木材和黄铜件取代，使用时不仅能够感受到木料的手感，黄铜的颜色也会在温度的影响下产生独特的光泽。设计团队还为 CROZ 配备了带有自然木纹的植鞣皮革带，木、铜、皮三者的组合相较透明版更让人眼前一亮。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/crozp2/croz-diy-digital-lomo-camera\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 899 港币。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007215949rET7Gz0pC9yZKHFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007215950ylbq0IEsmBpowgAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007215950nOX9JYKoTZUEkfDh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666411\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220017NdDGKjtXm8MvwaZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007215951XV7LjpZaQisA4PGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007215951M4zau6tBeOEr7D0F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p>          </p><h3>FreakishWATCH by Sabrina Fossi Design</h3><p>          </p><p>专营手工家居用品的意大利公司 <a href=\"http://www.sabrinafossi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sabrina Fossi Design</a> 最近以“适合每个人以及各种场合佩戴”为设计理念，打造了一款名为 FreakishWATCH 的腕表，预计将在三周后通过 Kickstarter 进行众筹。腕表分为黑色和黄色两款，它不仅具有极简风格的外观，所使用的材料也都具备轻质和纤薄的特征。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.sabrinafossi.com/freakishwatch\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>订阅它的相关信息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220830SmxwogkD7v0hFBfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.509780\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220830GXpmc8V6RtBYjKug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220830m3QCXW7HdojbgsOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610072208323azBZPd6TY51jXut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007220832jiyVodtv1pSLRcT6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Badeschoggi by Herr Bürli</h3><p>          </p><p>瑞士设计师 <a href=\"http://herrbuerli.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Herr Bürli</a> 最近为他妻子手工制作的肥皂 <a href=\"http://herrbuerli.ch/packaging/badeschokolade/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Badeschoggi</a> 设计了一套看上去颇具甜美气息的概念包装。Bürli 以巧克力为灵感将肥皂设计成了块状，并在纸盒的正面做出了镂空的效果以突出手工制作的特色。顾客能够透过透明的塑料片窥见宛如白巧克力般的产品本身，淡粉和淡蓝则刚好区分了玫瑰和薰衣草香型。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007223740jt0NCkvXIDWm93Rw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007223740MFimdw0K6uJQP5jA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007223740HdKJTfX16INjGCzb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610072237408Lhyw3PvRWOUEc04.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007223740n3GZOCKmRWk8aTv0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161007223740rqe2szpvCHFIV81y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}